    "en": {
      "title": "A clash at Kandakadu camp",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A tense situation has arisen between the inmates of the Welikanda Kandakadu Drug Rehabilitation Center and the Army following the mysterious death of an inmate this morning.",
        "Nearly 440 detainees are reported to have escaped during the clashes.",
        "The Army and the Police have been called in to control the situation, Welikanda Police said.",
        "The canopy of the body of the detainee who died under suspicious circumstances could not be obtained by the police or the army."
      ],
